This project is an attempt to build a timeline of historical events in the Late Medeival/Early Modern period

It uses the latest python, and a bunch of other resources pulled down by pyproject.toml

I've noticed some resources that shouldn't be there and the documentation is ... sketchy ... that's life, folks. 

The current problem is that I've tried scrolling by arrow keys and buttons but the timeline keeps being messed up. See screen captures in the folder screen captures
